videos.title: Duskmourn MTG Spoilers  A Busted Bestie, 5c Room Legend, New Legacy Finisher and More!
videos.description:
We're almost at the end of Duskmourn spoilers - tomorrow's the last day of previews and the full set should be out on Friday - but today we have some wild cards including a new 5C Legend, a green creature that might be the most broken card in the set and a possible new Legacy finisher from a Commander precon! Let's discuss!

Today's video is brought to you by Card Kingdom. You can pick up some Magic: the Gathering cards (and help support the show) at https://www.cardkingdom.com/mtggoldfish

More spoilers: https://www.mtgpreviews.com
